In Ammar Elementary School with older children, in addition to computer
skills and Microsoft Office software, they are also taught graphic software
such as Photoshop and Scratch game software.
Also, if it is observed that students have more capabilities, they will be
taught web design with simple and understandable concepts.

at the end of Mortazavi St., after Saheb-ol-Zaman.
